{"type": "article", "id": 53638, "title": "手写信、邮票都成了老古董，但设计师还是玩出了新意｜这个设计了不起", "description": "每个周末，《好奇心日报》都会找个主题为你寻找精彩设计。", "date": "2018-05-26T23:11:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 267, "name": "平面设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 6205, "name": "邮票"}, {"id": 50630, "name": "信封"}, {"id": 16376, "name": "明信片"}, {"id": 50631, "name": "Dream Giant"}, {"id": 50632, "name": "D-Bros"}, {"id": 50633, "name": "Andy Rementer"}, {"id": 50634, "name": "Cansu Merdamert"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 209, "image": "img/article/article_show/201805262053501027GVLbWzTROl8f.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; color: #0f1419; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #0f1419} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><p>用手写信通信、交流的人现在已经越来越少了。但是去到陌生的城市、景点，还是会有想要给家人、朋友寄明信片的冲动。这个周末，我们盘点了一组与邮票、信封、明信片甚至蜡封相关的设计，一起来看。</p><h3>Botanical Postcards by Cansu Merdamert</h3><p>伊斯坦布尔插画师 Cansu Merdamert 最近推出了一套植物主题的明信片，以手绘植物插画为特色，每张明信片上的植物种类不同。印在不同尺寸的非标准明信片用的天然手工纸上，不规则的毛边也为明信片添入一份手工制作的质朴气息，很特别。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180526205613fVZvoAXUGFkpN3zD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.422857\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/64465023/Botanical-Postcards\" rel=\"nofollow\">Behance</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Art stamps by Grayson Perry, Tracey Emin，Yinka Shonibare，Fiona Rae，Norman Ackroyd and Barbara Rae</h3><p>为了庆祝伦敦皇家艺术学院 250 周年，英国皇家邮政发行了一套六枚邮票，每一枚邮票都是由受人尊重的艺术家和院士设计的，包括 Grayson Perry，Tracey Emin，Yinka Shonibare，Fiona Rae，Norman Ackroyd 和 Barbara Rae。皇家邮政给到艺术家们一定自由发挥的空间，但也提出，这些作品不能有攻击性，或试图推动政治议程。</p><p>最终，艺术家们创作的风格各异，比如 Tracey 就画了她垂死的老母亲；Perry 创作了一幅向沃霍尔致敬的自画像；Yinka 在典型的英国雨伞的画面中注入了非洲版画的内容，最初的灵感来源是一张 1950 年代的英国人在雨中排队的照片。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180526205744JxzXT3kKS78M1Ql5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.557692\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180526205746wQS3orWIxLm7P9cd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180526205747aXTV6SIchvrlu12Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.546667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180526205747tNuSPlTaygis0eQd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.654696\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180526205747zDQu0fxlk4ysdjac.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>ALUMA by Oli Soden &amp; Charles Lo of Stamptitude</h3><p>ALUMA 被描述为“世界上第一个磁性蜡封”，最近正在 Kickstarter 上众筹。ALUMA 是同类产品中第一款采用革命性磁性配件的蜡封，允许用户在多个刻印头设计之间快速切换。ALUMA 这个名字，则来自于其细长的灰色坚实的铝质手柄，它改变了传统的蜡封形式，这个创新的磁性蜡封，实用又有趣。售价 450 港币，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/stamptitude/aluma-the-worlds-first-magnetic-wax-seal?ref=95ixdh\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805262059466jKudHBPs4recZAE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.637143\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180526205947CB3UrF1vGpMWjqts.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180526205947DcHIWf7m8nhroOJg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180526205948uoyHkzqvgx2p3C5L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.598529\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180526205948ptLKf2DmsJ14Xw8u.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Amore Tecnologico Stamps by Andy Rementer </h3><p>被意大利环绕的圣马力诺是世界第五小的国家，但却是世界上第一个开展邮政业务的国家，“邮票王国”的美誉早已名满天下。擅长卡通与插画的美国艺术家 Andy Rementer 基于“网上约会”这个主题，为圣马力诺邮政署设计了一系列新邮票，这也是继“ 3D 打印”主题邮票之后，Andy Rementer 与圣马力诺邮政署的第二次合作。</p><p>“我倾向于在我的作品中使用大胆的色彩和简单的形状，这些特质都很适合出现在小小的印制邮票上，”Andy Rementer 表示。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180526210112mD09Kj6vAUJcqyVl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.301105\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180526210113WsApUFehfJ89ItBE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.759669\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180526210113sLzWt3yrXlGvEAkT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.759669\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180526210114t2S0FeyckOEB6bAR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.767956\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180526210117v60UjpYdCRuBcA1S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.759669\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180526210120dZnM9VYz7s1BSkNc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.704420\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.itsnicethat.com/news/andy-rementer-online-dating-stamps-170616\" rel=\"nofollow\">It’s Nice That</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Booooon! Envelope by D-Bros</h3><p>每一次收到信，总会迫不及待地想要打开看里面的内容，可是有时候把信封撕坏了都会留下丑丑的痕迹。日本设计公司 D-Bros 推出一款名为 Booooon! 的信封，三张一组，每组信封都有三种颜色，各种颜色左上方分别画着飞机、汽车与火车，每一种交通工具后方都有一个 OPEN 字样的图示，等待拉开。</p><p>拉开后，所留下来的痕迹，很像是交通工具向前奔驰所留下来的长长的尾气、烟雾，看起来逗趣十足。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180526210208pnmrYI4Ako8eV5O3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.672000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180526210209Kp0mC8RbzMOHdogr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.828037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180526210209av4MGtg78sxOU30w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.660000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Headstart for Happiness by Dream Giant</h3><p>这是新加坡设计工作室 Dream Giant 为一对新人设计的婚礼邀请函和邮票套装，主视觉元素取自新加坡历史悠久的市政区。设计师试图唤起一种怀旧的情绪，也借用了复古风格的明信片的概念。</p><p>邀请函的内容用手写字体的形式呈现，以及老式明信片的扇贝边缘，都强化了手工质感。配套设计的两套邮票，也延续了邀请函的风格。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180526210658AecSBvGQLMVnWli3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.938333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180526210700ZFQsD2l3JLxg7ujp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.938333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180526210701xslAM52LDSvjcmhu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.938333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180526210703R7MbQUC9AuGZjzvp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.938333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180526210703ku02VXPn3pRlLyYH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.938333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}